b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2069,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Presenting 2.5-Year Anniversary Events!","message":"<div>The following events for the 2.5-year anniversary will start on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9dcec5a96ff74d28ea81cbd570f59293.png\\"><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>1. Announcing a Platinum Showcase! 5\\u2605 Gala Dragalia Adventurer Guaranteed!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>A Platinum Showcase where a 5\\u2605 Gala Dragalia adventurer available at the time of this summon showcase is guaranteed to appear in the tenfold summon will be held!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include the new adventurers from the Gala Dragalia showcase, which will be live at the same time.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Availability Period<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618207199\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><a href=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/2065\\">See here for more information.<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>2. Announcing Gala Dragalia!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5\\u2605 adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Availability Period<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1617343199\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><a href=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/2063\\">See here for more information.<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>3. Presenting 2.5-Year Anniversary Packs!<\/div><div>Anniversary packs will be available for a limited time under Value Packs in the Shop starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Availability Period<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618207199\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><a href=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/2071\\">See here for more information.<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>4. Daily Free Tenfold Summon!<\/div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, starts on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1617602399\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><a href=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/2067\\">See here for more information.<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>5. 2.5-Year Anniversary Bonus!<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/834da1621be8415588956ef7edde949e.png\\"><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get the following incredible rewards when you log in during the event duration!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Daily Rewards<\/div><div>Day 1: Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 2<\/div><div>Day 2: Mini Mercs &times; 1<\/div><div>Day 3: Rupie &times; 25,000,000<\/div><div>Day 4: Blessed Ethon Ashes &times; 20<\/div><div>Day 5: Wyrmite &times; 1,000<\/div><div>Day 6: 5\\u2605 Wyrmprint: Holywyrm&#39;s Advent &times; 1<\/div><div>Day 7: Eldwater &times; 100,000<\/div><div>Day 8: Damascus Ingot &times; 1<\/div><div>Day 9: Wyrmite &times; 1,000<\/div><div>Day 10: Sunlight Stone &times; 1<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618207199\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>In addition, the dragon Mini Hildy will be added to the fafnir medals section of the Treasure Trade.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The log-in bonus will be sent to you every day after 6:00 AM when you log in.<\/div><div>2. Gifts sent as log-in bonuses can only be accepted for a limited time.<\/div><div>3. The 5\\u2605 wyrmprint &quot;&quot;Holywyrm&#39;s Advent&quot;&quot; will be gifted directly to you instead of being sent to your goodie box.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>6. The Dawn of Dragalia Raid Event is Coming!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Don&#39;t miss this limited-time raid event. Take on event-specific quests to defeat the raid boss with no elemental attunement and earn rewards!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618207199\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><a href=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/2070\\">See here for more information.<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>7. Resetting the Social Reward in Co-op!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We will reset the number of times players can obtain the social reward, which can be obtained by playing co-op with another player for the first time, on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>After clearing a quest, you can get 50 wyrmite per player (up to 50 times). You can get a total of 2,500, so be sure to play co-op!<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>8. Champion&#39;s Road Campaign Endeavors!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Champion&#39;s Road Campaign endeavors will become available on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span>. Complete all of these limited-time endeavors during the event period, which lasts until <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618898399\\"><\/span>, and you can earn great items and a total of 5,000 wyrmite!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The endeavors include Clear High Mercury&#39;s Trial on Standard as well as Clear Ciella&#39;s Wrath on Standard, and the notification linked below contains tips on how to clear those quests. Do your best to complete as many of these endeavors as possible!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>If you do not have any adventurers who can be leveled up to complete the Raise an Adventurer to Lv. 80 endeavor, please wait for the raid event scheduled to start in the near future.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1585288800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618898399\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>9. Presenting 2.5-Year Anniversary Upgrade Events!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616824800\\"><\/span>, a triple drops event for Avenue to Power and a triple rupies event for Avenue to Fortune will be held alongside many other events such as co-op double drops for Advanced Dragon Trials and The Agito Uprising.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><a href=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/10061\\">See here for more information.<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1616643000,"prev_article_id":"2076","next_article_id":"2087","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9dcec5a96ff74d28ea81cbd570f59293.png","update_time":1616569663}}}'